<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Url-Prefix on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/url-prefix/</link><description>Recent content in Url-Prefix on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/url-prefix/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Blueprint registration error</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/flask/blueprint-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/flask/blueprint-error/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when Flask fails to register a Blueprint because of invalid naming, missing &lt;code&gt;url_prefix&lt;/code&gt;, or conflicts with existing route registrations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Blueprint name conflicts with another registered blueprint&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;URL prefix is missing or duplicates another blueprint&amp;rsquo;s prefix&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Blueprint is registered before the Flask app is fully initialized&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Route names clash when multiple blueprints define the same endpoint name&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Give each blueprint a unique name:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;from&lt;/span&gt; flask &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; Blueprint
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;user_bp &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; Blueprint(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;users&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, __name__)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;admin_bp &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; Blueprint(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;admin&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, __name__)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="2"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Specify unique URL prefixes:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;app&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;register_blueprint(user_bp, url_prefix&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;/users&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;app&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;register_blueprint(admin_bp, url_prefix&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;/admin&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="3"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use the &lt;code&gt;name&lt;/code&gt; parameter to avoid module conflicts:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;app&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;register_blueprint(user_bp, name&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;user_module&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="4"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prevent endpoint name collisions with the &lt;code&gt;name&lt;/code&gt; parameter:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;from&lt;/span&gt; flask &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; Blueprint
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;api &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; Blueprint(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;api&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, __name__)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@api.route&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;/status&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;status&lt;/span&gt;():
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; {&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;status&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;ok&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;app &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; Flask(__name__)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;bp1 &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; Blueprint(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;api&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, __name__)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;bp2 &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; Blueprint(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;api&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, __name__) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# same name&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;app&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;register_blueprint(bp1, url_prefix&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;/api/v1&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;app&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;register_blueprint(bp2, url_prefix&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;/api/v1&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# ValueError: The name &amp;#39;api&amp;#39; is already registered&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/flask/config-error/"&gt;Configuration error&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>